#

Simple Chicken Tortilla Soup

40 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

none

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-protein

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

soup

Tags:

soupeasyquickcomfort food

Description

A warm and comforting soup packed with tender chicken, vegetables, and crispy tortilla strips.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 2 pieces
  • chicken broth: 4 cups
  • canned diced tomatoes: 1 can (14.5 oz)
  • black beans: 1 can (15 oz)
  • corn: 1 cup
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • tortilla chips: 2 cups
  • avocado: 1, diced
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lime: 1, juiced
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • chili powder: 1 tsp
